data.description: Nice home and lot package in popular Virginia Beach neighborhood. The home features a re-done kitchen open to the family room, separate dining room, wet bar for entertaining, huge laundry room and tasteful accents throughout. Sliding glass doors take you out the screened-in porch and large deck. Small creeks runs along the back of the lot for privacy and there is also an oversized shed that offers many possibilities - hobby shop, workshop, storage area or just convert it to a nice man-cave. It's impressive.  Stratford Chase is centrally located in the city and within a short drive to I-64, all the major military bases, Towne Center and many local favorite restaurants, recreational facilities and shopping areas. This one is nice!
